  "_meta": {
    "source": "W5-27 FF2 canonical sequence v4 (SPEC-ficha-medica.md AMENDMENT 2026-07-12 FF2-A/B). Reorders v3 to the FF2-A sequence and removes linked_appointment (Marcação respectiva) and neurological_tests (Testes Neurológicos) per FF2-B. v1/v2/v3 immutable (CLAUDE.md rule 5); records referencing them render their original structure.",
    "reviewed_by": "W5-27 (Claude Opus 4.8)",
    "version_note": "v4 — FF2-A property order realized (Peso+Altura thin card, Alertas+CID row, bodychart, observations, mobilidade, mobilidade_observacoes, consultation_reason[required], tratamento, treatment_plan, treatment_objectives, diagnostico, relief_aggravation, systems_review, health_problems/Outros, clinical_history, special_tests). FF2-B removals: linked_appointment + neurological_tests absent. Twelve AI keys + template=osteopathy identity UNCHANGED (consultation_reason, relief_aggravation, clinical_history, systems_review.{neurological,cardiovascular,respiratory,gastrointestinal,urological_gynecological,endocrine}, treatment_objectives, treatment_plan, observations) — W5-13 compat stays green. Titles unchanged. bodychart carries the W5-25 shapes/legend + W5-26 optional intensity (Path A undeclared passthrough key, no schema change). W5-26 reconcile: Path A held (no pre-existing v4). created_at read-only, no date input (ruling B). Bumped not edited: v3 immutable once referenced."
  }
